        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/41197/web_resize__large.png"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Hailing from Águeda, Portugal, Danças Ocultas is an accordion quartet with a unique sound, crafted over the past 35 years. The band creates minimalist, lyrical and deeply evocative music with just four diatonic accordions. They tap into folk music, nuevo tango and chamber music to weave delicately captivating soundscapes of what some have called “impressionist folk.” \n\nTheir most recent album, Inspirar (2025), earned a spot among the top world music albums in Europe. \n\nDanças Ocultas captivates and charms audiences, creating a sweetly..."
      }
    ],
