    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "La Pambelé    | A new approach to old-school salsa  |  Thu, Jul 23, 2026, 7:30 pm | Babs Asper Theatre"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/41186/pambele_horizontal_5_juan_diego_rivas__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "El español sigue al texto en inglés\n\nLa Pambelé is a salsa brava orchestra redefining Colombia’s tropical and alternative music landscape by revisiting the sonic traditions of 1970s salsa brava while infusing them with contemporary lyrical narratives. \n\nTheir sound bridges nostalgia and modernity, what one of Colombia’s leading media outlets described as “a new approach to old-school salsa.” The ensemble’s nine musicians bring together a rich instrumentation: piano, congas, flute, trumpet, timbales, trombone, bongó, cowbell, baby bass, and vocals, crafting a dynamic..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
